1979 - 2010
"His smile lights the sky at night, his freckles are the stars
he wraps his soul around us all, and it's then we hear his laugh""Š
╗Major A.A.E. (Trof') Trofimov,
soldier and architect (1921-2006)
and his beloved wife, Jean Hope,
interior designer and gardener (1930-2008)
both enjoyed celebrating life to the full."Š
